{"tid":483162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【港獨】香港民族陣線成員招募","createTime":"2017-11-29T00:43:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-06T14:45:53.000Z","uid":28366,"like":84,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"022df5e19ff1123031e4ee927ec26b855eec2634","tid":483162,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T00:43:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/083820_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F083820_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=6488c252&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">【你輸過，但你想不想贏？】</span><br />\n<br />\n三年前，除了頭盔、雨傘以及血肉之軀，我們一無所有<br />\n面對黑警精良的裝備、持之以恆的訓練，我們兵敗如山倒<br />\n沒錯，就是兵敗如山倒<br />\n被打得頭破血流，一無所得，這可說徹頭徹尾的失敗。<br />\n<br />\n然而，失敗並不可怕，真正可怕的是沉醉在那些所些甚麼「公民覺醒」丶「遍地開花」的精神鴉片當中，為三年前的失敗沾沾自喜。撫心自問，如果可以再來一次，香港人能否改變結果？<br />\n不，今日的我們依然弱小。<br />\n你漸漸忘記忘記了那一夜對著硝煙與槍口的我們何等無力<br />\n甚至忘記了你的憤怒<br />\n失敗不可怕，可怕在習慣失敗<br />\n<br />\n勝利非一朝一夕，亦非唾手可得，<br />\n只有不斷變強，方能看見勝利的曙光。<br />\n如果你希望改變<br />\n如果你不想再經歷失敗的苦澀<br />\n請加入我們的行列當中<br />\n讓我們聚沙成塔，化作摧枯拉朽的洪流，粉碎殖民暴政，重掌我們的家園。<br />\n<br />\nTelagram: <a href=\"https://t.me/Goebbelshknf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FGoebbelshknf&d=KrzM3%2B12F8yz3rimzNYpnDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=9a80c056\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Goebbelshknf</a><br />\n<br />\nEmail: [url]Hongkongnationalfront@gmail.com[/url]<br />\n<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HK.NationFront/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHK.NationFront%2F&d=KrzM3%2B12F8yz3rimzNYpnDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=fcab8efa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HK.NationFront/</a>"},{"pid":"b50c9ac44642f910eddb79bd40d86398eb38096a","tid":483162,"uid":28366,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T00:45:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e774fbdb639a9934f4409bb795fceecc1e252ffa","tid":483162,"uid":37733,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T01:08:19.000Z","msg":"終於做野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dacf606fb4994e0b4ee10bff71debe905755efa9","tid":483162,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T01:09:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>終於做野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6661d48ade35bb120ce6853dfaa5ec6fd0c837a8","tid":483162,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T01:10:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9215a3af334aa0c1b8530fedbf9d7ed433872e47","tid":483162,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T01:20:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e8c50bc7f6693419aff33cae2d9783081ff3c42","tid":483162,"uid":19552,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T01:34:25.000Z","msg":"睇黎好快建國成功<br />\n堡主好多軍火"},{"pid":"48cd31c332ce102a7a3615e816d797c92523ff99","tid":483162,"uid":28366,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T01:37:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇黎好快建國成功<br />\n堡主好多軍火</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5103be9e31543b9ac554a63b8f85deeef5464cc8","tid":483162,"uid":28366,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T01:38:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3ohhwef0GQQt24XLEI/giphy.gif\"